esheet\"><script language=\"javascript\" src=\"/system/resource/js/ajax.js\"></script><form name=\"_newscontent_fromname\">\n<div class=\"left fl\">\n                        <div class=\"img slow fl\">\n                                                    <img src=\"/__local/A/59/1D/2D3D9F3B56BA50D01A69E807FC0_36109D10_7ECD.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-bottom: #39b54a 3px solid;\">\n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"con fr\">\n                            <h3>徐萌</h3>\n                            <dl><dd>清华大学基础医学院  研究员</dd>\n                            \n                            </dl>                            \n                            <p>\n                                <b>Contact Us：</b><br>\n                                Tel: +86-10- 62799959<br>\n                                E-mail:  michellexu@tsinghua.edu.cn<br>\n                                \n                            </p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n<div class=\"right fr\">\n \n       \n\n       \n\n\n\n\n<div id=\"vsb_content_501\"><div class=\"v_news_content\">\n<p class=\"vsbcontent_start\"><span style=\"color: rgb(112, 48, 160);\"><b>教育经历：</b></span></p>\n<p>中国科学院，生物物理研究所, 感染与免疫科学中心</p>\n<p>博士，细胞生物学 2007- 2012</p>\n<p>首都医科大学,</p>\n<p>学士，药学 2003-2007</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(112, 48, 160);\"><b>工作经历</b><b>:</b></span></p>\n<p>基础医学院（原医学院基础医学系） 研究员 2017至今</p>\n<p>芝加哥大学(The University of Chicago)</p>\n<p>助理研究员 2016-2017</p>\n<p>博士后学者 2013-2016</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(112, 48, 160);\"><b>代表性论文：</b></span></p>\n<p>1) Yu Wang#; Shaocun Zhang#*; Na Kang; Lihui Dong; Haochen Ni; Sichen Liu; Siankang Chong; Zhenglin Ji; Zhengpeng Wan; Xiangjun Chen; Fei Wang; Yun Lu; Baidong Hou; Pei Tong; Hai Qi; <b>Meng Michelle Xu</b>*; Wanli Liu*; Progressive polyadenylation and m6A modification of Ighg1 mRNA maintain IgG1 antibody homeostasis in antibody-secreting cells, <b><i>Immunity</i></b>, 2024, 57(11): 2547-2564</p>\n<p>2) Yi Liu#; Guanghao Liang#; Hongjiao Xu#; Wenxin Dong#; Ze Dong#; Zhiwei Qiu; Zihao Zhang;Fangle Li; Yue Huang; Yilin Li; Jun Wu; Shenyi Yin; Yawei Zhang; Peijin Guo; Jun Liu; Jianzhong Jeff Xi; Peng Jiang; Dali Han*; Cai-Guang Yang*; <b>Meng Michelle Xu</b>*; Tumors exploit FTO-mediated regulation of glycolytic metabolism to evade immune surveillance, <b><i>Cell Metabolism</i></b>, 2021, 33(6): 1221-1233</p>\n<p>3) Lihui Dong#; Chuanyuan Chen#; Yawei Zhang#; Peijin Guo; Zhenghang Wang; Jian Li; Yi Liu; Jun Liu; Renbao Chang; Yilin Li; Guanghao Liang; Weiyi Lai; Mengxue Sun; Urszula Dougherty; Marc B. Bissonnette; Hailin Wang; Lin Shen; <b>Meng Michelle Xu</b>*; Dali Han*; The loss of RNA N6-adenosine methyltransferase Mettl14 in tumor-associated macrophages promotes CD8+ T cell dysfunction and tumor growth, Cancer Cell, 2021, 39(7): 945-957.E10</p>\n<p>4) Dali Han#*; Jun Liu#; Chuanyuan Chen; Lihui Dong; Yi Liu; Renbao Chang; Xiaona Huang; Yuanyuan Liu; Jianying Wang; Urszula Dougherty; Marc B. Bissonnette; Bin Shen; Ralph R. Weichselbaum; <b>Meng Michelle Xu</b>*; Chuan He*; Anti-tumour immunity controlled through mRNA m6A methylation and YTHDF1 in dendritic cells, <b><i>Nature</i></b>, 2019, 566: 270-274</p>\n<p>5) <b>Meng Michelle Xu</b>; Yang Pu; Dali Han; Yaoyao Shi; Xuezhi Cao; Hua Liang; Xiang Chen; Xiao-Dong Li; Liufu Deng; Zhijian J. Chen; Ralph R. Weichselbaum; Yang-Xin Fu; Dendritic Cells but Not Macrophages Sense Tumor Mitochondrial DNA for Cross-priming through Signal Regulatory Protein alpha Signaling,<a></a> <b><i>Immunity</i></b>, 2017, 47(2): 363-373</p>\n<p>6) Xiaojuan Liu#; Yang Pu; Kyle Cron; Liufu Deng; Justin Kline; William A. Frazier; Hairong Xu; Hua Peng; Yang-Xin Fu*; <b>Meng Michelle Xu</b>#; CD47 blockade triggers T cell-mediated destruction of immunogenic tumors, <b><i>Nature Medicine</i></b>, 2015, 21(10): 1209-15</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(112, 48, 160);\"><b>其他论文：</b></span></p>\n<p>7) Menghao You; Jingjing Liu; Jie Li; Ce Ji; Haochen Ni; Wenhui Guo; Jiarui Zhang; Weiwei Jia; Zhao Wang; Yajiao Zhang; Yingpeng Yao; Guotao Yu; Huanyu Ji; Xiaohu Wang; Dali Han; Xuguang Du*; <b>Meng Michelle Xu*</b>; Shuyang Yu*; Mettl3-m6A-Creb1 forms an intrinsic regulatory axis in maintaining iNKT cell pool and functional differentiation, <b><i>Cell Reports</i></b>, 2023, 42(6):112584</p>\n<p>8) <b>Meng Xu</b>#; Mingyue Liu#; Xuexiang Du; Sirui Li; Hang Li; Xiaozhu Li; Ying Li; Yang Wang; Zhihai Qin; Yang-Xin Fu*; Shengdian Wang*; Intratumoral Delivery of IL-21 Overcomes Anti- Her2/Neu Resistance through Shifting Tumor-Associated Macrophages from M2 to M1 Phenotype, <b><i>Journal of Immunology</i></b>, 2015, 194(10): 4997-5006</p>\n<p>9) <b>Meng Xu</b>; Xuexiang Du; Mingyue Liu; Sirui Li; Xiaozhu Li; Yang-Xin Fu*; Shengdian Wang*; The tumor immunosuppressive microenvironment impairs the therapy of anti-HER2/neu antibody, <b><i>Protein &amp; Cell</i></b>, 2012, 3(6): 441-449</p>\n<p>10) Xiaofei Zhang; Tingting Cong; Lei Wei; Bixi Zhong; Xiaowo Wang; Jin Sun; Shuxia Wang; <b>Meng Michelle Xu</b>; Ping Zhu*; Hong Jiang*; Jianwei Wang*; YTHDF3 modulates hematopoietic stem cells by recognizing RNA m6A modification on Ccnd1, <b><i>Haematologica</i></b>, 2022, 107(10)</p>\n<p>11) Yuzhu Hou; Hua Liang; Enyu Rao; Wenxin Zheng; Xiaona Huang; Liufu Deng; Yuan Zhang; Xinshuang Yu; <b>Meng Xu</b>; Helena Mauceri; Ainhoa Arina; Ralph R. Weichselbaum*; Yang- Xin Fu*; Non-canonical NF-κB Antagonizes STING Sensor-Mediated DNA Sensing in Radiotherapy, <b><i>Immunity</i></b>, 2018, 49(3): 490</p>\n<p>12) Hua Liang#; Liufu Deng#; Yuzhu Hou; Xiangjiao Meng; Xiaona Huang; Enyu Rao; Wenxin Zheng; Helena Mauceri; Matthias Mack; <b>Meng Xu</b>; Yang-Xin Fu*; Ralph R. Weichselbaum* ; Host STING-dependent MDSC mobilization drives extrinsic radiation resistance, <b><i>Nature Communications</i></b>, 2017, 8(1736)</p>\n<p>13) Yang Pu; <b>Meng Xu</b>; Yong Liang; Kaiting Yang; Yajun Guo; Xuanming Yang *; Yang-Xin Fu*; Androgen receptor antagonists compromise T cell response against prostate cancer leading to early tumor relapse, <b><i>Science Translational Medicine</i></b>, 2016, 8(333): ra47</p>\n<p>14) Dali Han#; Xingyu Lu#; Alan H. Shih#; Ji Nie; Qiancheng You; <b>Meng Michelle Xu</b>; Ari M. Melnick; Ross L. Levine*; Chuan He* ; A Highly Sensitive and Robust Method for Genome- wide 5hmC Profiling of Rare Cell Populations, <b><i>Molecular Cell</i></b>, 2016, 63(4): 711-719</p>\n<p>15) Liufu Deng; Hua Liang;<b> Meng</b> <b>Xu</b>; Xuanming Yang; Byron Burnette; Ainhoa Arina; Xiao-Dong Li; Helena Mauceri; Michael Beckett; Thomas Darga; Xiaona Huang; Thomas F. Gajewski; Zhijian J. Chen; Yang-Xin Fu*; Ralph R. Weichselbaum*; STING-Dependent Cytosolic DNA Sensing Promotes Radiation-Induced Type I Interferon-Dependent Antitumor Immunity in Immunogenic Tumors, <b><i>Immunity</i></b>, 2014, 41(5): 843-852</p>\n<p>16) Liang Cheng#; Xuexiang Du#; Zheng Wang; Jianqi Ju; Mingming Jia; Qibin Huang; Qiao Xing; <b>Meng Xu</b>; Yi Tan; Mingyue Liu; Peishuang Du; Lishan Su*; Shengdian Wang*; Hyper-IL-15 suppresses metastatic and autochthonous liver cancer by promoting tumour-specific CD8(+) T cell responses, <b><i>Journal of Hepatology</i></b>, 2014, 61(6): 1297-1303</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(112, 48, 160);\"><b>受邀综述：</b></span></p>\n<p>17) Dali Han;<b> Meng Michelle Xu</b>; RNA Modification in the Immune System, <b><i>Annual Review of Immunology</i></b>, 2023, 41(1): 73-98</p>\n<p><a></a>18) <b>Meng Michelle Xu</b>; Yuan Zhang; Yang-Xin Fu; The Role of Adaptive Immunity in the Efficacy of Targeted Cancer Therapies, <b><i>Trends in Immunology</i></b>, 2016, 37(2): 141-153</p>\n<p>19) <b>Meng Michelle Xu</b>; Yang Pu; Ralph R. Weichselbaum *; Yang-Xin Fu*; Integrating conventional and antibody-based targeted anticancer treatment into immunotherapy, <b><i>Oncogene</i></b>, 2017, 36(5): 585-592</p>\n<p>#共同第一作者</p>\n<p>*共同通讯作者</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(112, 48, 160);\"><b>经费支持（在研项目）:</b></span></p>\n<p>1. 国家自然科学基金委员会, 重大项目, T2495272，TCR-T细胞的智能设计与高效合成， 2025-01-01至2029-12-31,444万元，在研，参与</p>\n<p>2. 国家自然科学基金委员会, 重大项目, 22293052, 金属参与的免疫调控机制,2023-01-01 至 2027- 12-31, 528.6万元, 在研, 参与</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(112, 48, 160);\"><b>经费支持（结题项目）</b></span></p>\n<p>3. 国家自然科学基金委员会, 优秀青年科学基金项目, 81922054, 肿瘤免疫, 2020-01-01 至 2022-12- 31, 120万元, 结题, 主持</p>\n<p>4. 国家自然科学基金委员会, 面上项目, 31870890, 信使RNA-m6A修饰对树突状细胞抗肿瘤免疫反应的调控机制研究, 2019-01-01 至 2022-12-31, 60万元, 结题, 主持</p>\n<p>5. 北京市自然科学基金委员会, 重点研究专题, Z200023, 单细胞解析消化道肿瘤中免疫细胞功能耗竭的机制和免疫治疗策略, 2020-10 至 2024-10, 300万元, 结题, 主持</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(112, 48, 160);\"><b>奖励及荣誉</b></span></p>\n<p class=\"vsbcontent_end\">2019年 国家优秀青年基金获得者</p>\n</div></div><div id=\"div_vote_id\"></div>\n\n\n</div>\n\n\n  \n\n\n\n      \n\n</form>\n\n                      \n                    </div>\n                                      \n                </div>\n          <section class=\"n_sanji\">\n<ul style=\"    height: 44px;\">\n    <li><a href=\"../../szdw/jcyxy.htm\" title=\"教职员工\">教职员工</a></li>\n    <li><a href=\"../../szdw/jzjs.htm\" title=\"兼职教授\">兼职教授</a></li>\n</ul>\n                  \n                </section>\n\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"mianbao\">\n            <div>\n     您现在的位置： \n                        <a href=\"../../index.htm\">首页</a>\n               <i>&gt;</i>\n                <a href=\"../../szdw/jcyxy.htm\">师资队伍</a>\n               <i>&gt;</i>\n                <a href=\"../../szdw/jcyxy.htm\">基础医学院</a>\n               <i>&gt;</i>\n                <a href=\"../../szdw/jcyxy/jyxl.htm\">教研系列</a>\n               <i>&gt;</i>\n                <a href=\"../../szdw/jcyxy/jyxl/myx.htm\">免疫学</a>\n               <i>&gt;</i>\n                正文\n</div>\n\n\n\n\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"content_li1\"></div>\n        </div>\n    \n</section>\n<script>\n$('.miso_hd ul').miso({\n    autoplay:false,\n    slidesToShow: 3,\n    waitForAnimate: false,\n    asNavFor:$('.mi